--WebAppBoundary--

### 5. Check if file exists
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Files/exists?filePath={{filePath}}

### 6. Get file info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Files/info?filePath={{filePath}}

### 7. Delete file
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Files?filePath={{filePath}}

